Test2::Event::Diag(3perl)                                                            Perl Programmers Reference Guide                                                            Test2::Event::Diag(3perl)

NAME
       Test2::Event::Diag - Diag event type

DESCRIPTION
       Diagnostics messages, typically rendered to STDERR.

SYNOPSIS
           use Test2::API qw/context/;
           use Test2::Event::Diag;

           my $ctx = context();
           my $event = $ctx->diag($message);

ACCESSORS
       $diag->message
           The message for the diag.

SOURCE
       The source code repository for Test2 can be found at http://github.com/Test-More/test-more/.

